{"tid":1391813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非 同我入來！！！","createTime":"2019-07-31T14:22:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T19:54:36.000Z","uid":274504,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2ac368b13f4b5a67ca63073c773a69f4f4726050","tid":1391813,"uid":274504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:22:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>和理非人士 注意 係時候做下野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">到咗呢個時候<br />\n身邊仲係有好多人話唔敢罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一來公司無人講，二來又唔敢得罪老細，三來更加唔想無咗份工<br />\n可能你身邊都有好多呢d人<br />\n或者你就係<br />\n但其實你地仲有好多野可以做<br />\n坐地鐵番工既朋友 <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">番工時日日阻地鐵 阻到政府理為止 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n每人做一次<br />\n其他人唔知你係唔小心 定係特登 風險極低<br />\n特別響大圍站,荔景站,九龍塘站,大子站,旺角站,金鐘站,油塘站<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好睇小自己 我地人很多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n希望你地支持既周圍share <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nshare 到個個都收到</span>"},{"pid":"7f61cb72a3ac86584f481a36f79c7900b60c3f83","tid":1391813,"uid":295481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:24:39.000Z","msg":"香港人加油<br />\n<br />\n5/8 九巴不合作運動 正式啟動！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/abDpOOU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/abDpOOU</a><br />\n<br />\nTG group<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/OmURXQ09pQAlcm8-nJTDLA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FOmURXQ09pQAlcm8-nJTDLA&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFkPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=8d55f628\" data-auto-li